<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 28 at 6:22PM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...LIGHT SNOW TRANSITIONS TO DRIZZLE THIS EVENING...
Light snow showers taper off by 8 PM EDT, with a transition to
drizzle/freezing drizzle for the rest of the evening. Given air
temperatures in the low 30s, slippery conditions remain possible,
especially on untreated roadways. Continue to use caution while
driving this evening and allow extra time to reach your
destination.</description>
